Sprite File (.spr) Block Diagram
.-----------------------------------.
|    Signature (53h 50h 52h 00h)    |
|-----------------------------------|
|           Atlas  Header           |
|            (20  bytes)            |
|                                   |
|-----------------------------------|
|          Animation Table          |
|          (Variable size)          |
|                                   |
|-----------------------------------|
|            Atlas  Data            |
|          (Variable size)          |
|                                   |
'-----------------------------------'

Atlas Header
.-----------------------------------.
|      Sprite Width  (4 bytes)      |
|-----------------------------------|
|      Sprite Height (4 bytes)      |
|-----------------------------------|
|      Atlas Columns (4 bytes)      |
|-----------------------------------|
|       Atlas Rows  (4 bytes)       |
|-----------------------------------|
| Offset To Start Of Atlas (4bytes) |
'-----------------------------------'

Animation Table
.-----------------------------------.
|  Number of Animations (4 bytes)   |
|-----------------------------------|
|            Animation 0            |
|          (Variable size)          |
|-----------------------------------|
|            Animation 1            |
|          (Variable size)          |
|-----------------------------------|
|                 .                 |
|                 .                 |
|                 .                 |
|-----------------------------------|
|            Animation N            |
|          (Variable size)          |
'-----------------------------------'

