|-----------------------------------|
|    Keyframe 0 index (4 bytes)     |
|-----------------------------------|
|   Keyframe 0 duration (4 bytes)   |
|-----------------------------------|
|    Keyframe 1 index (4 bytes)     |
|-----------------------------------|
